data.description: This home is located in a on a quiet cul-de-sac in great neighborhood and is move in ready!  As you enter you will appreciate the newer LVP flooring throughout the home as well as the fresh paint. The kitchen features a large eating bar with quartz countertops, SS appliances and a pantry. The family room has a slider taking you to the amazing 17'x39'covered deck with a built in BBQ, lighting and ceiling fans for you to enjoy the outdoors all year long. The fully fenced back yard is private, quiet and pristinely maintained with raised beds and a large shed on the side for storing lawn equipment and toys. Upstairs there are 4 spacious bedrooms. The primary features an en-suite bath with 2 sinks and a walk-in shower as well as a walk-in closet. The large RV pad and drive-way offers plenty of parking space. New roof in 2022! Convenient to shopping and high-tech, come see it today! [Home Energy Score = 4. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10222634]
